==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rubytail
<hw>Ru"by*tail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A European gold wasp (<spn>Chrysis ignita</spn>) which has the
under side of the abdomen bright red, and the other parts deep bluish
green with a metallic luster. The larva is parasitic in the nests of
other wasps and of bees.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ruby-tailed</ent>⟦br⟧
